text: Kuzino () is a rural locality (a village) in Bolshesosnovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km south-west from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Kuzino, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai
